              <h3>University of California, Berkeley</h3>
              <p class="degree">Master of Analytics (STEM)</p>
              <p class="degree">Major in Electrical Engineering & Computer Science (EECS)</p>
              <p class="duration">Aug 2022 - Mar 2023</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

